        (Magnus Hagander)
       </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   在不支持Unix套接字连接的平台上拒绝
   <link linkend="auth-pg-hba-conf"><filename>pg_hba.conf</></link>中的
   <literal>local</>行(Magnus Hagander)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
        Formerly, such lines were silently ignored, which could be surprising.
        This makes the behavior more like other unsupported cases.
       </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   先前，默默忽略这样的行，这可能是令人惊讶的。
