        clauses to be attached to <command>INSERT</>, <command>UPDATE</>,
        <command>DELETE</> statements (Marko Tiikkaja, Hitoshi Harada)
       </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   允许<link linkend="queries-with"><literal>WITH</></link>子句被附属于
   <command>INSERT</>，<command>UPDATE</>，
   <command>DELETE</>语句(Marko Tiikkaja, Hitoshi Harada)
</para>
